description: BandCombCompression: Table storing band combination compression configuration parameters for specific cells at a given time.  dateTime: Timestamp of the configuration; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3: Redundant identifier; Id4: Redundant identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; BandCombCompression.requestedBandCombCompression: Requested band combination compression; BandCombCompression.requestSkipFallbackComb: Flag to skip fallback combinations; BandCombCompression.requestReducedFormat: Flag to use reduced format; BandCombCompression.requestMaxCCsDL: Maximum number of downlink component carriers; BandCombCompression.requestedFreqBandsFiltered: List of filtered frequency bands; BandCombCompression.requestMaxCCsUL: Maximum number of uplink component carriers; BandCombCompression.requestReducedIntNonContComb: Flag for reduced non-contiguous combinations; BandCombCompression.bandCombCompressionId: Unique identifier of the band compression configuration.
